{"tid":2317794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙一個動物園有四隻獅子感染了新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-12-09T00:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T00:43:15.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb99022bafc1067b7df1faff3d28da9cc9496fc","tid":2317794,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:09:38.000Z","msg":"第一波時唔係有人話動物唔會中招既？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=415875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415875&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=7fb6d68c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415875&h=d2bc905b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=415875</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獸醫部門說，巴塞羅那一個動物園有三隻雌性和一隻雄性獅子出現輕微症狀，經測試證實對新冠病毒呈陽性，動物園內兩名員工亦證實染病，當局正調查這幾隻獅子是如何受感染。<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約市的布朗克斯動物園今年四月亦有七隻獅子和老虎證實感染了新冠病毒，牠們現時已經全部康復。"},{"pid":"66d66e678136198bc75822cd1f6966c2f3f913e7","tid":2317794,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"個時講未有證據"},{"pid":"fbf077073dd4af90c7bff6b85cb7d11b18edcf28","tid":2317794,"uid":41342,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:10:56.000Z","msg":"右上果隻咳得好西利咁"},{"pid":"add994057de5bb24c786b9d39b418092b0d869fb","tid":2317794,"uid":132585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf077073dd4af90c7bff6b85cb7d11b18edcf28","tid":2317794,"uid":41342,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:10:56.000Z","msg":"右上果隻咳得好西利咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T00:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f3c5ed01f3429962dd2efc4c2f7f9e831dc9bf","tid